    <fr:title text="abelian group structure on the W-bar construction">abelian group structure on the W-bar construction</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  Suppose the simplicial group <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> is abelian, then the <fr:link href="/forest/hmlg-0021/" title="W-bar construction" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/hmlg-0021/" display-uri="hmlg-0021" type="local">W-bar construction</fr:link> still has an abelian group structure, by multiplication element-wise.
</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
